      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BERGER-Wendy. Taken from us too soon. Our hearts go out to her beloved husband, Ross; sister and brother, Jennifer and Kenny; stepmother, Chris; and mother Ida. Wendy was an extraordinary force of nature. Family, friends, patients colleagues-she touched us all. Services Monday, 1:15 PM at Riverside Memorial Chapel, 76 St. and Amsterdam Ave. Ellen Rubin &amp; David Shapiro</p>
      </block>
